nodes.text: The Best of Star Wars Insider Volume 2

The Best of Star Wars Insider Volume 2 is the second volume in Titan Comics' The Best of Star Wars Insider bookazine series, which collects material previously published in Star Wars Insider magazine. It was released on June 21, 2016.
Second volume of the Star Wars Insider, featuring content previously printed in the Star Wars Insider magazine.
